exceptions.tactic: rewrite <- (plusA_eqA_comp_r A A0 A0 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs a A0 A0 eq_a_A0).
exceptions.exn: In environment A : Set A0, A1 : A eqA : A -> A -> Prop plusA : A -> A -> A invA : A -> A minusA, multA : A -> A -> A divA : A -> forall b : A, ~ eqA b A0 -> A cs : CoefStructure A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA eqA_dec : forall a b : A, {eqA a b} + {~ eqA a b} eqA_trans := CoefStructure.eqA_trans A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs : Relation_Definitions.transitive A eqA eqA_sym := CoefStructure.eqA_sym A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs : Relation_Definitions.symmetric A eqA a : A eq_a_A0 : eqA a A0 The term "A" has type "Set" while it is expected to have type "A".

original: intros a eq_a_A0. rewrite <- (plusA_eqA_comp_r A A0 A0 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA cs a A0 A0 eq_a_A0). rewrite plusA_A0. reflexivity.
